JobPK: It is the unique indentifier for each job (primary key)
JobNumber: It is used to identify the brokerage, shipment and warehouse jobs
TransactionMonth: This is the month when the customer transaction happened
TransactionYear: This is the year when the customer transaction happened
FYMonth: It is the combination of FY year and month (FY-18-Dec)
FYQuarter: It is the combination of FY year and quarter (FY-18-Q4)
FYYear: It is the combination of FY year (FY-25)
CountryPK: It is the unique indentifier for country (primary key)
CountryGroup: It is the customer's country's group
CompanyPK: It is the unique indentifier for company (primary key)
CompanyCode: It is the customer's company code
BranchPK: It is the unique indentifier for branch (primary key)
BranchCode: It is the customer's branch code
DeptPK: It is the unique indentifier for department (primary key)
DeptCode: It is the customer's department code
JobStatus: It is the status of the shipment/job
JobRevenueStatus: It is the payment status of shipment/job
TransportMode: It is the transport mode of the shipment or job (e.g. AIR, COU, FSA, NOJ, ROA, SEA)
ContainerMode: It is the Container Mode of the shipment or job (e.g. BBK, BCN, CNT, CON, FCL, FTL, JHB, LCL, LSE, LTL, NOJ, OBC, ROR, SCN, UNA)
Direction: It is the direction of shipment like import, export, NOJ or others
JobType: It is the type of the job like shipment job, warehouse job or brokerage job
JobLevel1: It tells whether job is freight or non-freight
JobLevel2: It tells whether job is CrossTrade, Destination, Freight, Origin, Others, PassThrough, Transportation, Warehouse
JobLevel3: It tells whether job is CrossTrade, Customs-Export, Customs-Import, Destination Job, Freight-P2P, Origin Job, Others, PassThrough, Transportation, Transportation-Export, Transportation-Import, Warehouse
ProductLevel1: It tells whether product level 1 is Air Export, Air Import, Cartage-Delivery, Cartage-FCL, Cartage-Others, Cartage-Pickup, Cartage-SeaExport, Cartage-SeaImport, Customs, Others, Sea Export, Sea Import
ProductLevel2: It tells whether product level 2 is Cartage-Delivery, Cartage-FCL, Cartage-Others, Cartage-Pickup, Cartage-SeaExport, Cartage-SeaImport, FCL, LCL, LSE
ProductLevel3: It tells whether product level 3 is NULL or values like BBK, BCN, CNT, CON, FCL, FTL, JHB, LCL, LSE, LTL, OBC, ROR, SCN, UNA
OriginETD: It is the estimated time of departure of job from origin country
DestinationETA: It is the estimated time of arrival of job to destination country
ActualVolume: It is the total volume of job
UnitOfVolume: It is the unit of volume, such as tons, kg etc.
ActualChargeable: It is the Actual Chargeable amount of job
ChargeableUnit: It is the Actual Chargeable unit of job such as KG or M3
AirVolumeInTons: It is volume of job in transport mode air in tons
AirVolumeInCBM: It is volume of job in transport mode air in cubic meters
SeaVolumeLCL: It is volume of job in transport mode sea in LCL
SeaVolumeFCL: It is volume of job in transport mode sea in FCL
SeaVolumeFCLTEU: It is volume of job in transport mode sea in FCLTEU
FinalVolumeinCBM: It is Final volume of job in cubic meters
CustomerGroup: It is the customer name group
CustomerGroupName: It is the customer group name
CustomerLeadGroup: It is the customer lead group
CustomerLeadGroupName: It is the customer lead group name
ConsolNo: It is the consolidated job number
ConsolATA: It is the actual time of arrival of shipment
ConsolATD: It is the actual time of departure of shipment
OriginCountry: It is the origin country of shipment
DestinationCountry: It is the destination country of shipment
Incoterm: This column defines the international commercial terms (Incoterms) agreed between the buyer and seller
OriginContinent: It is the origin continent of the shipment
DestinationContinent: It is the destination continent of the shipment
CSTAmount: It is the cost of the shipment
WIPAmount: It is work in progress amount of job
REVAmount: It is the revenue amount of job
JobProfit: It is the profit of job
